  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,52,"SeeHelaman 8:15."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,53,"SeeDoctrine and Covenants 6:36."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,54,"Jesus Christ taught us the importance of sacred ordinances, such as baptism (seeJohn 3:5), the sacrament (seeDoctrine and Covenants 59:9), and the endowment and sealing ordinances of the temple (seeDoctrine and Covenants 124:39–42)."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,55,"SeeDoctrine and Covenants 124:29–32."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,56,"SeeLuke 8:43–44."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,57,"Mark 5:28."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,58,"SeeDoctrine and Covenants 88:63."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,59,"When the faithful woman touched the Savior’s clothing, He instantly responded, “I perceive thatvirtue[from the Greekdunamis,meaning “power”] is gone out of me” (Luke 8:46; emphasis added)."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/drawing-the-power-of-jesus-christ-into-our-lives,President Russell M. Nelson,60,"“The Spirit of God,”Hymns,no. 2."
